  "texts": [
    "2021), SVT-Net 9 (Fan et al. 2022), TransLoc3D 10 (Xu et al.",
    "2021), MinkLoc3Dv2 11 (Komorowski 2022), OREOS (Schaupp et al. 2019), Scan Context 12 (Kim and Kim 2018), DiSCO 13 (Xu et al.",
    "2021), BEVPlace 14 (Luo et al. 2023), PIC-Net (Lu et al.",
    "2020), MinkLoc++ 15 (Komorowski et al. 2021), CORAL (Pan et al.",
    "2021), AdaFusion 16 (Lai et al. 2022)) according to the categories of feature-based, projection-based, and multimodal-based methods.The evaluation is based on the AR@1 and AR@1% metrics."
